comments: Jones (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hield (IND) and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Taylor (IND) legally contests DiVincenzo's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Haliburton (IND) momentarily grasps Jones' (SAC) jersey while trying to defend around the pick being set. The contact is marginal and does not affect Jones' FOM.
After Mitchell (SAC) dislodges the pass, causing a loose ball, both players make contact with it and force it into the backcourt where Brissett (IND) legally regains control.
Barnes (SAC) makes contact with Taylor's (IND) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) grasps and releases Haliburton (IND) off-ball as the pass is entered, and the contact is marginal.
Haliburton (IND) hooks Barnes (SAC) at the start of his drive, and the contact affects his ability to defend.
Haliburton's (IND) left foot stays in the frontcourt.
DiVincenzo (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Haliburton (IND).
Brissett (IND) cleanly dislodges the ball from Jones (SAC) during the rebound,
Brissett (IND) establishes himself in DiVincenzo's (SAC) path when incidental contact occurs as DiVincenzo slips the contact when he passes.
Haliburton (IND) makes contact with the ball last before it goes out of bounds on the sideline.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Hield (IND) loses control of the ball while dribbling and it goes out of bounds on the sideline.
Lyles (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Haliburton (IND) and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Anderson (IND) brushes Mitchell's (SAC) arm as Haliburton (IND) makes contact with the ball to slightly dislodge it during the drive.
